</CENTER><P><A HREF='index.htm'>Return to Index</A>.</P><CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 
CELLPADDING=5 WIDTH=90%><TR><TD></TD><TD><CENTER><H1>Chapter 3</H1></CENTER>    
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V1><H4>1</H4></TD><TD><P>Wherefore when we 
could no longer forbear, we thought it good to be left at Athens alone;</P></TD>
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V2><H4>2</H4></TD><TD><P>And sent Timotheus,    
our brother, and minister of ELOHIYM, and our fellowlabourer in the gospel of   
MASHIYACH, to establish you, and to comfort you concerning your faith:</P></TD> 
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V3><H4>3</H4></TD><TD><P>That no man should be  
moved by these afflictions: for yourselves know that we are appointed           
thereunto.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V4><H4>4</H4></TD><TD><P>For 
verily, when we were with you, we told you before that we should suffer         
tribulation; even as it came to pass, and ye know.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD         
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V5><H4>5</H4></TD><TD><P>For this cause, when I could no     
longer forbear, I sent to know your faith, lest by some means the tempter have  
tempted you, and our labour be in vain.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A      
NAME=V6><H4>6</H4></TD><TD><P>But now when Timotheus came from you unto us, and 
brought us good tidings of your faith and charity, and that ye have good        
remembrance of us always, desiring greatly to see us, as we also to see you:</P>
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V7><H4>7</H4></TD><TD><P>Therefore,        
brethren, we were comforted over you in all our affliction and distress by your 
faith:</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V8><H4>8</H4></TD><TD><P>For now 
we live, if ye stand fast in the ADONAY.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A     
NAME=V9><H4>9</H4></TD><TD><P>For what thanks can we render to ELOHIYM again    
for you, for all the joy wherewith we joy for your sakes before our EL;</P></TD>
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V10><H4>10</H4></TD><TD><P>Night and day        
praying exceedingly that we might see your face, and might perfect that which   
is lacking in your faith?</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V11><H4>      
11</H4></TD><TD><P>Now ELOHIYM himself and our Father, and our ADONAY YAHSHUA   
MASHIYACH, direct our way unto you.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V12>
<H4>12</H4></TD><TD><P>And the ADONAY make you to increase and abound in love   
one toward another, and toward all men, even as we do toward you:</P></TD></TR> 
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V13><H4>13</H4></TD><TD><P>To the end he may         
stablish your hearts unblameable in holiness before ELOHIYM, even our Father,   
at the coming of our ADONAY YAHSHUA MASHIYACH with all his saints.</P></TD></TR>
